{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require temporary workers be offered full employment contracts after two years",
        "additional_details": "The uncertainty and lack of rights resulting from temporary work puts a mental and physical strain on people. I would like the Government to require that temporary workers be offered a permanent role after they have been with the same company for more than two years.",
        "background": "I have been a temporary worker for nearly 7 years. I do the exact same work as the full-time employees but get none of the company benefits they get (contractual sick pay, bonuses, Company share scheme). I am often worried that they could tell me not to come back to work with no notice.",
